Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.64,0:00:03.40,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是靈樹森林的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.40,0:00:04.11,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,還有小孩子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.11,0:00:05.80,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那個大個男人是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.84,0:00:08.00,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我們好像變成觀賞物了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.52,0:00:10.40,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,因為前排的人醒目啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.15,0:00:12.99,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,快看 是妖精
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.32,0:00:15.94,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然帶著妖精這樣奇怪的生物
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.94,0:00:17.21,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,果然是真正的魔女啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.27,0:00:21.12,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 我可不想和你一起相提並論
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.48,0:00:23.95,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那邊的兩位哪個是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.26,0:00:27.16,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不 大家 魔女大人在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.45,0:00:29.25,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,幹嘛 鬼鬼祟祟的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.92,0:00:30.46,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,大家好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.46,0:00:31.55,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.55,0:00:32.54,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那樣的小屁孩是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.88,0:00:35.42,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,摩根 這到底在開什麼玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.42,0:00:37.55,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不 不是玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.68,0:00:40.22,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,啊啊 也難怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.68,0:00:42.89,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,來一發魔法讓他們開開眼如何
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.89,0:00:44.89,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這些傢伙就不會不服氣了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.89,0:00:46.52,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這我做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.52,0:00:49.66,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,為了引人注目而使用魔法是不可以的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.19,0:00:52.56,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我早說了 村長
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.98,0:00:53.96,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,祭司大人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.96,0:00:54.78,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,是僧侶嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.78,0:00:57.08,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,事情複雜了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.53,0:01:00.61,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,即使依靠魔女這種不可靠的迷信
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.61,0:01:03.79,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,也無法解決目前的情況
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.91,0:01:08.20,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,而且摩根 你讓那樣的小丫頭扮成魔女
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.20,0:01:13.00,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,是打算消除自己一人苟活回來的自責感吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.00,0:01:14.46,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你這樣太膚淺了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.88,0:01:15.75,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我怎麼會
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.25,0:01:19.51,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這副打扮 你們是旅行藝人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.76,0:01:22.26,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,旅途中被摩根哀求了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.80,0:01:25.16,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不管你們是來巡演的還是幹什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.39,0:01:28.93,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那些魔獸可不是你們能對付的來的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.35,0:01:30.93,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,最好馬上離開這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.44,0:01:32.81,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,可是祭司大人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.81,0:01:36.40,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那個男人仔細看看不是很強壯嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.40,0:01:37.63,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不用趕走也可以吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.63,0:01:38.44,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不可
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.44,0:01:41.61,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這是神明大人給予這個村莊的試煉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.86,0:01:43.78,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我們唯有祈禱和忍耐
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.24,0:01:46.58,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,回去吧 別管他們了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.58,0:01:49.66,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我們好不容易來了 沒進門就被趕走嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.66,0:01:50.83,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,好像傻瓜一樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.91,0:01:55.67,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,小姑娘即使是演戲或假扮也不要如此
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.77,0:01:58.80,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,如果這裡是聖都 你會被處以火刑的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.25,0:02:02.72,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,魔女隻是墮落和邪惡的象徵
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.09,0:02:05.93,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我們帶著病人和小孩長途跋涉已經很疲憊了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.93,0:02:08.18,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,可以的話希望借宿一晚
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.18,0:02:10.52,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 現在這種時候
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.52,0:02:12.89,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那個姑娘在做祈求恢復的巡禮
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.26,0:02:16.88,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,向巡禮者施捨是寺院的規矩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.07,0:02:19.82,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你們是死是活我也不會再管了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.82,0:02:21.42,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,承蒙你的大恩
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.72,0:02:23.15,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,快看 那把劍
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.15,0:02:24.32,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,是真傢伙嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.38,0:02:25.68,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那個左臂
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.86,0:02:28.33,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,村長 請給他們準備房間
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.99,0:02:30.58,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你想了妙招呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.58,0:02:32.41,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,反正我肚子餓了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.41,0:02:35.17,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,用眼睛好好感受吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.17,0:02:38.75,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這次邂逅對你到底意何在
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.43,0:04:13.69,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,大家請把這個綁到手指上
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.04,0:04:15.85,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,頭髮嗎 是你的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.22,0:04:17.48,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼把 頭髮
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.85,0:04:19.48,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,為了能使用念話
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.84,0:04:20.98,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,就是心靈感應
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.98,0:04:22.15,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,念話
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.15,0:04:23.44,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,真是可疑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.44,0:04:24.73,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,低能猴子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.73,0:04:26.28,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,誰是猴子 你這個傻瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.86,0:04:33.47,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡使用的是施術時持有施術對象一部分的被稱為感染魔術的技術
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.47,0:04:36.35,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,使用指甲頭屋之類的對人下詛咒嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.44,0:04:40.58,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,任何人只要到某種程度 都可能進行直接的思想交互
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.79,0:04:45.67,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,但是這就需要有很高的氣 靈氣的磁力的連接
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.05,0:04:48.97,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,能相連的只有你嗎 其他人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.97,0:04:52.43,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,突然就和沒有修行的人聯繫是不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.40,0:04:59.15,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,因此這次和獸鬼的作戰中 希望大家都聽我的指揮
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.18,0:05:00.41,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這是當然的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.43,0:05:02.56,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你說什麼 別開玩笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.90,0:05:05.82,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,誰要被你這種小丫頭使喚
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.82,0:05:07.65,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這是最合適的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.94,0:05:12.97,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,能把握整個戰況並傳達給大家的只有我這個魔法師
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.66,0:05:18.62,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,確實如此 在獸鬼上魔女才是專家
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.83,0:05:22.46,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,就這樣吧 本來她就是對付鬼的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.75,0:05:25.21,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,明白 三等兵向指揮敬禮
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.63,0:05:28.86,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,在遇敵前逃跑會被槍斃的 猴子三等兵
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.42,0:05:30.19,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.19,0:05:32.30,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那孩子怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.30,0:05:33.51,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,想單獨待一會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.43,0:05:40.89,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,見鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.56,0:05:43.60,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你在練劍嗎 小兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.60,0:05:45.90,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,但是一個人可不安全啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.12,0:05:48.15,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,老大爺你又在幹嘛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.48,0:05:51.99,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,本想給你們的晚餐準備些魚
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.99,0:05:52.86,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,但是不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.45,0:05:56.03,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,算了 還有番薯湯再忍耐會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.16,0:05:59.54,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,說起來這裡真是個小村莊呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.54,0:06:03.75,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,在這種山谷裡 能見陽光的時間不到半天吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.73,0:06:11.55,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我爺爺那輩這個村莊是連著街道的 據說很熱鬧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.55,0:06:13.55,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,現在就像你看見的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.47,0:06:18.10,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,就算這麼說 也不想默默等死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.10,0:06:20.06,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我對你們很期待啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.56,0:06:25.06,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,小兄弟你為何要和他們一起旅行呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.35,0:06:27.86,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,是那位黑色劍士的侍從嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.86,0:06:31.53,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不對 我在做武者的修行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.94,0:06:35.66,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,格斯大哥和我有約定要教我劍術
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.37,0:06:39.58,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那位劍士很強呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.58,0:06:41.95,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,竟能揮舞那樣巨大的劍
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.11,0:06:45.79,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,對吧 他強得就和怪物一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.25,0:06:47.79,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你很崇拜他嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.13,0:06:50.50,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,崇拜 別這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.50,0:06:51.80,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是利用他而已
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.76,0:06:56.30,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,作為我目前的目標而努力
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.14,0:06:59.85,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你家裡人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.07,0:07:03.48,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那種事都無所謂了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.48,0:07:05.48,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你這個旁人不會明白的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.44,0:07:08.31,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你又是怎麼回事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.31,0:07:11.98,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這把年紀還不顧家人去找魔女
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.61,0:07:15.04,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,還有那些村人是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.11,0:07:20.12,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,對拚命去找魔女的你竟然那麼排斥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.12,0:07:22.12,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,真是群薄情的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.62,0:07:25.79,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你不如也離開這裡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.79,0:07:28.88,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,留在這種小地方也沒什麼好的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.06,0:07:33.08,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡長眠著我的家人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.92,0:07:35.22,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,被獸鬼殺害的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.72,0:07:38.01,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不 是更久前死的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.09,0:07:46.73,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我感謝把村子命運寄託給我的村民 因此我沒有怨言
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.73,0:07:53.66,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我反而更感謝他們 讓我在死前能再見到那位魔女
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.65,0:07:56.99,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,男人都是這樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.99,0:08:00.16,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我小時候也幻想過
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.36,0:08:03.91,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,說著要去找魔女要去抓妖精
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.91,0:08:08.21,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,然後拋下家裡的工作去深山裡森林裡閒逛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.71,0:08:13.00,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,就像你說的 我也曾要離開這個小村莊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.00,0:08:17.13,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,自己坐著船從布利達尼斯向海洋出發
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.63,0:08:20.30,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,一直夢想著這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.22,0:08:23.68,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,直到母親病倒
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.02,0:08:28.10,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那時的事已經記不清了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.52,0:08:32.23,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,只知道等察覺到時已經在森林深處迷路了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.73,0:08:37.00,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我是為救母親而去找魔女的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.74,0:08:42.28,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,彷彿在夢中一樣 我到了那個地方
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.58,0:08:48.12,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那時我用帶回家的藥救回了媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.50,0:08:51.79,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,但她已經很衰老了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.38,0:08:57.17,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,從那以後我就在家做事再也沒去過森林了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.38,0:09:00.34,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,回過神時已經這把年紀了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.74,0:09:05.90,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,然後時光流逝 記憶也模糊了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.85,0:09:08.98,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,真的曾見過她嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.10,0:09:17.69,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,但魔女卻在森林深處等著我 和那時一模一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.17,0:09:20.36,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這些對就足夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.82,0:09:22.73,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 別說了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.80,0:09:26.15,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,對我這樣的年輕人不要說那種陳年舊事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.15,0:09:28.17,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,最近的年輕人真是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.17,0:09:32.42,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,把那麼普通的一個夢當成年輕時的大事的你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.73,0:09:35.67,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,和正在實現野心的我不要相提並論
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.67,0:09:37.60,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我的野心會長毛的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.67,0:09:39.01,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,再見了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.01,0:09:42.88,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你在這裡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.76,0:09:47.26,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那個小鬼對你很依賴呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.22,0:09:54.65,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,獸鬼來襲時 村民們能躲藏的就是這個寺院吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.94,0:09:57.48,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,果然只能在這布陣了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.32,0:10:00.78,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,總之 我必須要振作
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.19,0:10:04.07,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 寺院坐落的這個地方
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.47,0:10:08.70,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你們
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.76,0:10:11.04,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,滾出去 魔女
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.04,0:10:14.46,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,祭司大人說了 魔女和獸鬼是一個樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.46,0:10:16.13,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,讓人火大
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.72,0:10:23.05,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,在勘察陣地嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.60,0:10:24.88,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.55,0:10:29.43,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你那時是不是對那個僧侶有話要說
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.43,0:10:31.93,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,對那個臭僧侶才不想說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.43,0:10:34.27,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不只是那個僧侶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.69,0:10:38.52,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我認為現在世上的人都錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.15,0:10:40.82,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,坐落著寺院的這個山丘
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.92,0:10:44.52,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,過去曾是祭祀這片土地的精靈的神殿遺蹟
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.04,0:10:47.95,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,法王廳的寺院大都如此
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.95,0:10:52.16,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,踐踏精靈信仰的聖地然後建立起來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.67,0:10:57.61,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,現在法王廳的教只是用來誇耀自己權力的道具
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.40,0:11:01.10,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,人們禮讀著神的名字互相爭鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.32,0:11:03.63,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,禮讀著神的名字尋求救贖
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.34,0:11:11.35,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,自己想要忘卻的東西說不定反而是救贖自己的關鍵所在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.52,0:11:16.48,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡面也有你們魔女嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.19,0:11:21.94,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我的師傅過去曾在這附近的村落生活
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.86,0:11:24.69,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,奔走於貧困的村莊之間
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.69,0:11:26.96,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,向人們傳達精靈的話語
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.26,0:11:31.62,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,一邊向他們傳教季節的事一邊治病救人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.41,0:11:35.83,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,師傅的魔法救治了很多人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.10,0:11:40.54,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,但是隨著法王廳的教團擴展到這一帶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.94,0:11:42.88,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,每個村莊開始建起了寺院
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.42,0:11:45.60,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,簡直如同翻臉一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.60,0:11:49.72,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,人們驅趕師傅 把她趕到了森林裡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.21,0:11:56.68,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,從那之後師傅就在森林中躲避世人並隱居起來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.89,0:12:01.20,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,而現在竟然好像沒發生過那種事一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.96,0:12:03.23,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我不能原諒這些
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.79,0:12:07.03,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,要不是師傅吩咐誰要救這個村子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.68,0:12:08.94,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼不做就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.28,0:12:09.66,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,什
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.72,0:12:12.49,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你要是沒有那個意向的話
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.70,0:12:14.91,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,就沒有必要為了那些討厭的人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.44,0:12:17.04,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,以身犯險了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.96,0:12:19.79,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那個婆婆就要死了不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.19,0:12:21.42,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那就更要這樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.75,0:12:24.67,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,被人說了就算不喜歡也照做
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.67,0:12:25.96,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這可是小孩的做法
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.05,0:12:30.81,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,真是個沒禮貌還吊兒郎當的人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.20,0:12:33.71,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我可是不情不願的來的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.56,0:12:37.24,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這個男人不可能是我的命運
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.31,0:12:38.31,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,絶對
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.84,0:12:41.10,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 不要亂動
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.25,0:12:42.27,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,法爾納塞小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.40,0:12:46.84,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,給聽不懂話的法爾納塞小姐綁頭髮是不是沒有意義啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.97,0:12:49.40,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,但是史爾基小姐說要綁的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.87,0:12:53.40,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,說念話是靠印象傳導的 我也不太懂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.64,0:12:55.62,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不要動
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.04,0:12:58.38,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,說實話這次的獸鬼退治
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.38,0:13:01.08,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不說起來這次旅行本身
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.29,0:13:04.84,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我都認為應該停止
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.92,0:13:08.38,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 卡思嘉小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.36,0:13:12.34,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.66,0:13:16.97,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,真是變樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.60,0:13:19.68,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這是我辦不到的事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.64,0:13:22.17,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,要是能看見這個笑容的話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.32,0:13:24.20,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,應該算是值得吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.73,0:13:28.14,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,風的精靈
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.24,0:13:30.90,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不被任何東西束縛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.28,0:13:32.91,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,能吹到任何地方
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.49,0:13:35.83,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,真是諷刺啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.49,0:13:38.95,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這是和我最無緣的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.38,0:13:46.46,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.81,0:13:47.67,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.42,0:13:52.01,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,獸鬼來了 都來寺院
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.72,0:13:53.64,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才那是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.64,0:13:54.33,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,難道說
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.59,0:13:55.43,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,是心靈傳送
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.17,0:13:56.99,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,塞爾彼高
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.99,0:13:58.01,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,法爾納塞小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.28,0:14:11.40,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,獸鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.63,0:14:13.15,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼回事那個數量
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.15,0:14:15.07,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,要一口氣吃光我們啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.07,0:14:17.24,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,趕緊跑吧這裡也不妙了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.31,0:14:18.79,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,比起這個吹號
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.01,0:14:27.54,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,念話馬上就來了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.79,0:14:29.42,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這東西確實方便
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.75,0:14:31.42,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,總之我們趕緊去寺院
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.80,0:14:38.35,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,塞爾彼高 想想史爾基小姐的話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.35,0:14:39.48,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,想明白點
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.47,0:14:40.56,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.56,0:14:43.23,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那個 想像 想像
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.15,0:14:48.32,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,拜託你們了 精靈們啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.96,0:14:58.81,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,趕緊跑
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.84,0:14:59.99,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.08,0:15:07.38,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,做得好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.71,0:15:09.92,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,說真的 有這個就能放心了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.93,0:15:12.25,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,魔法 真正的魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.75,0:15:15.68,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡 就你一個人出風頭
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.68,0:15:17.68,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不要出手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.82,0:15:18.91,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,上吧 火焰喲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.35,0:15:21.76,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,一匹就夠了 一匹
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.03,0:15:25.08,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 有效果
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.08,0:15:27.07,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,快跑啊 要被吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.07,0:15:33.57,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,杯水車薪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.57,0:15:34.40,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.01,0:15:40.31,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那些傢伙把受傷的伙伴吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.31,0:15:42.45,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不想變那樣就跑起來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.04,0:15:44.95,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,卡思嘉小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.12,0:15:51.92,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.34,0:15:59.30,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那個法爾納塞小姐會為了別人挺身而出
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.80,0:16:03.77,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,看來銀的退魔作用生效了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.22,0:16:07.44,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我來打開退路 趕緊跑到寺院去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.89,0:16:09.31,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,大家 趕緊進去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.60,0:16:11.52,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,看啊 有人被包圍了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.52,0:16:13.50,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,是那些魔女的同行者
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.50,0:16:15.65,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,為了能讓我們逃走用身體擋住獸鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.65,0:16:17.49,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那樣就沒救了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.49,0:16:19.28,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,太愚蠢了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.28,0:16:20.62,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我早說過了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.66,0:16:24.87,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋 那些傢伙不是人能對付的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.69,0:16:58.95,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,趁現在 跑到寺院
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.65,0:17:01.92,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,看到了嗎 祭司大人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.27,0:17:04.00,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,好厲害 幹掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.00,0:17:06.59,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,有那個那個人的話就能從獸鬼手上保護村子了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.60,0:17:08.20,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,好厲害 那傢伙好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.20,0:17:10.21,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,搞不懂哪邊是怪物了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.67,0:17:12.46,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,的確不像一般人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.13,0:17:18.76,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這也是那個人在精神能輕易影響物質的狹間彷徨的結果嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.17,0:17:20.17,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,還是說
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.80,0:17:23.51,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,纏在劍周圍的那個影子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.32,0:17:25.82,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,準備好了嗎 依巴蕾拉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.84,0:17:26.81,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,妥妥的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.08,0:17:29.48,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,在你說的方位上都貼好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.48,0:17:30.31,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,符咒
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.73,0:17:32.15,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,在緊張
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.48,0:17:33.81,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我說大家
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.44,0:17:37.36,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,接下來我要用魔法在這個寺院張開防壁
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.90,0:17:40.07,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,全員趕緊進去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.59,0:17:41.82,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這個遭報應的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.82,0:17:44.53,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,村長 趕緊讓那個女孩從房頂下來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.53,0:17:46.08,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 那個
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.08,0:17:47.38,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,魔術是真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.40,0:17:48.41,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我親眼看見了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.41,0:17:51.96,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那個女孩的同伴隔空砍死獸鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.96,0:17:54.38,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那個劍士大人的同伴們嗎 那麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.17,0:17:59.13,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,對對 腳踏實地腳踏實地
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.97,0:18:03.22,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,尤得·海恩 班·海恩
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.22,0:18:04.19,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,趕緊住手
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.35,0:18:05.97,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,使不得 使不得啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.98,0:18:08.64,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,在這個神的面前做這種邪惡之事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.64,0:18:10.60,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,趕緊從這裡下去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.60,0:18:12.88,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,史爾基是為了誰在做這些事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.02,0:18:15.86,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,欸 我叫你停下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.36,0:18:17.82,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你才是要住手
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.57,0:18:20.78,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那個孩子正在保護村子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.78,0:18:22.24,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你不明白嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.24,0:18:23.20,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你閉嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.20,0:18:24.99,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,就算生命能延續下去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.99,0:18:29.20,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,但是靠邪門歪道苟且偷生還有什麼意義
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.70,0:18:31.08,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這是天命啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.04,0:18:34.29,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這個男人 和我一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.16,0:18:36.67,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,和過去的我一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.46,0:18:40.59,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,仗著神的名義 把人逼上死路
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.34,0:18:44.76,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我沒有反駁的資格
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.81,0:18:53.52,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,光說你也不懂嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.84,0:18:55.36,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,阻止這個人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.37,0:18:58.48,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,誦讀咒文的史爾基正在神遊天外呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.86,0:19:00.48,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,請把手放開
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.48,0:19:01.60,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不要打擾我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.05,0:19:15.96,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.46,0:19:17.87,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,被包圍了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.37,0:19:20.34,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,法爾納塞小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.34,0:19:21.00,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,卡思嘉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.88,0:19:24.97,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你們趕緊去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.97,0:19:26.55,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡我一個就夠
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.84,0:19:28.97,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,裡面的人和女人們拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.97,0:19:30.81,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白了 拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.56,0:19:32.81,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我的份也一起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.76,0:19:40.90,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋躲開 過不去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.95,0:19:56.08,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,欸 看見了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.08,0:19:58.37,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,跳過我們 不對 飛過去的？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.37,0:20:00.38,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不愧是我們風之軍團
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.38,0:20:02.38,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你們也秀下身手呀
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.00,0:20:05.38,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,伊斯多洛 這裡暫時交給你了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.51,0:20:09.18,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,要坦然接受 不能恐懼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.30,0:20:11.14,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,卡思嘉小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.72,0:20:21.60,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,真是愚蠢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.61,0:20:23.02,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,史爾基
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.73,0:20:25.03,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,喔 神明啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.28,0:20:27.03,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,請引導我到您的身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.91,0:20:35.04,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才就是最後的了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.82,0:20:38.17,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,真實的 一群一群的沒完沒了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.38,0:20:40.17,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,史爾基那小鬼在幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.58,0:20:42.38,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這下不上不行了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.38,0:20:44.44,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你的本事說實話
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.44,0:20:46.84,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋 這才是關鍵時刻
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.01,0:20:52.89,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不好 身體被劍帶走了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.55,0:20:54.39,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,騙人的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.59,0:20:55.56,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,在這種地方
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.19,0:21:01.31,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,老爺子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.52,0:21:02.77,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,摩根
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.69,0:21:08.57,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 說你們啊 不能只靠小孩子和老頭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.57,0:21:10.07,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.53,0:21:14.24,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,老爺子  喂
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.57,0:21:15.74,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,由虛空中
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.74,0:21:20.41,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,把陸 海 空 火的透明的四人之王召喚至此
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.96,0:21:22.96,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,以此陣保吾身周全
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.96,0:21:26.09,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,當溫暖的守護的防禦之火點亮之後
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.21,0:21:35.26,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,令所有災禍 不會加之吾身
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.06,0:21:38.93,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,本·蓋普勒 馬魯可圖
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.27,0:21:41.50,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,馬忒·本 蓋土魯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.44,0:21:47.94,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,本·歐蘭
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.15,0:21:49.94,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,法爾納塞小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.84,0:22:08.84,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,獸鬼們 都碎了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.63,0:22:11.09,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這個光輝是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.87,0:22:15.93,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,傷口在癒合
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.80,0:22:18.36,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣就有救了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.00,0:22:22.56,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這就是 那傢伙的魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.81,0:00:18.27,DefaultUp,NTP,0,0,0,,這傢伙真沒禮貌
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.44,0:00:24.27,DefaultUp,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.76,0:01:22.26,DefaultUp,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.21,0:05:26.75,DefaultUp,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.35,0:05:29.42,DefaultUp,NTP,0,0,0,,你說誰猴子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.62,0:14:39.47,DefaultUp,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.19,0:18:05.52,DefaultUp,NTP,0,0,0,,我說 你幹什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.52,0:18:07.80,DefaultUp,NTP,0,0,0,,正忙的呢 不能打擾她
Comment: 0,0:22:28.99,0:22:31.46,EDCht,,0,0,0,,/--------ED---------/
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.70,0:22:49.15,EDCht,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,150)}緋紅序幕  緩緩拉開
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.15,0:22:53.10,EDCht,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,150)}笑談之間  揭開舞台
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.10,0:22:57.03,EDCht,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,150)}台上一切  皆為戲劇
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.03,0:23:00.45,EDCht,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,150)}循序漸進  如詩如畫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.45,0:23:10.04,EDCht,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,150)}一字之差  終局俱變
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.04,0:23:18.52,EDCht,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,150)}索然無味  其為傳說
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.10,0:23:23.84,EDCht,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,150)}利慾之心  隱於夜中
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.84,0:23:27.91,EDCht,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,150)}日升之前  一觸即發
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.91,0:23:32.58,EDCht,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,150)}純真羽翼  散落人間
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.58,0:23:37.28,EDCht,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,150)}應著之色  是黑是白
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.28,0:23:39.36,EDCht,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,150)}不得而知  好奇尚異
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.36,0:23:43.24,EDCht,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,150)}餘音裊裊  不絕於耳
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.24,0:23:47.16,EDCht,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,150)}何人願聞  何人可應
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.16,0:23:52.31,EDCht,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,150)}虛浮年華  何需再度
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.70,0:22:49.15,EDJap,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,150)}鮮明な赤の緞帳を引く
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.15,0:22:53.10,EDJap,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,150)}歓声の中  舞台へ上がる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.10,0:22:57.03,EDJap,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,150)}全て予定調和の戯曲
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.03,0:23:00.45,EDJap,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,150)}狂いは無い  絵画の様に
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.45,0:23:10.04,EDJap,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,150)}たった一字が欠けた時に結末は変わる
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.04,0:23:18.52,EDJap,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,150)}呆気無い程に  それが 物語
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.10,0:23:23.84,EDJap,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,150)}夜に隠したambition  greed
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.84,0:23:27.91,EDJap,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,150)}朝が来る前に放て
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.91,0:23:32.58,EDJap,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,150)}無邪気に散り降る羽
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.58,0:23:37.28,EDJap,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,150)}染まるべき色は白か黒か
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.28,0:23:39.36,EDJap,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,150)}知らない  知りたい
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.36,0:23:43.24,EDJap,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,150)}木霊するostinato
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.24,0:23:47.16,EDJap,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,150)}誰か聴いて  誰か応えて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.16,0:23:52.31,EDJap,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,150)}仮初の日々はもう要らない
Comment: 0,0:02:53.35,0:02:55.35,OPCht,,0,0,0,,/--------OP---------/
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.35,0:03:03.17,OPCht,,0,0,0,,刻下的烙印如何磨滅
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.67,0:03:12.63,OPCht,,0,0,0,,任憑他人道長短  殊死之斗又何曾徒勞
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.66,0:03:22.97,OPCht,,0,0,0,,暗啞了的嘶吼  依舊在耳畔激盪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.54,0:03:29.22,OPCht,,0,0,0,,笑至盡頭之人不是我  亦無怨無悔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.22,0:03:33.13,OPCht,,0,0,0,,唯願能夠守護你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.40,0:03:38.77,OPCht,,0,0,0,,誅盡來敵戰至終
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.77,0:03:41.46,OPCht,,0,0,0,,逆天而行破宿命
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.46,0:03:46.40,OPCht,,0,0,0,,思思纏繞神之手
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.40,0:03:50.92,OPCht,,0,0,0,,欲斷枷鎖魂難斷
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.27,0:03:56.70,OPCht,,0,0,0,,若能終結一切以戰止戈
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.70,0:04:00.21,OPCht,,0,0,0,,焚盡我身又何妨
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.71,0:04:08.58,OPCht,,0,0,0,,困獸猶鬥  逆境之中尋生存
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.35,0:03:03.17,OPJap,,0,0,0,,\h\h\h\h\h\h\h刻まれた烙印は  最早消せはしないと
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.67,0:03:12.63,OPJap,,0,0,0,,足掻くだけ時間の無駄だと  誰が言おうと
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.66,0:03:22.97,OPJap,,0,0,0,,また聞こえてくる叫び  声にもならない声で
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.54,0:03:29.22,OPJap,,0,0,0,,最後に笑うのはおれじゃなくていい
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.22,0:03:33.13,OPJap,,0,0,0,,そこにおまえがいれば
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.40,0:03:38.77,OPJap,,0,0,0,,戦いの果てまで辿り着くため
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.77,0:03:41.46,OPJap,,0,0,0,,運命(さだめ)を越えて
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.46,0:03:46.40,OPJap,,0,0,0,,断ち切れない  神の手でも
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.40,0:03:50.92,OPJap,,0,0,0,,結んだ絆と魂を
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.27,0:03:56.70,OPJap,,0,0,0,,戦いの果てまで辿り着くため
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.70,0:04:00.21,OPJap,,0,0,0,,すべてを懸けて
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.71,0:04:08.58,OPJap,,0,0,0,,足掻き続けて　生き抜いてみせるだけ
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.67,0:24:06.50,Preview,,0,0,0,,{\an7}這也是報應嗎 還是…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.76,0:24:11.84,Preview,,0,0,0,,我是為了保護他人才挺劍奮起的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.26,0:24:15.43,Preview,,0,0,0,,{\an9}正合我意! 你們這些大猴子們
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.81,0:24:19.89,Preview,,0,0,0,,{\an9}比起百人斬來說不算什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.64,0:24:23.60,Preview,,0,0,0,,{\an9}好想再見你一面啊 好久不見
